title: SkyBlock Z (v1.0)

crawledImageUrls.text:
Skyblock Z it?s just plain classic skyblock? With some different islands, generators, spawners and maybe more in the future! This first version was quickly made in one day, but it will receive updates.
SkyBlock Z is the same thing as a normal SkyBlock map, but here you can explore islands, find generators, maybe even structures (in the future), and so much more. It contains pretty much what SkyBlock maps has. You spawn in a island, with a chest containing basic items and blocks! The map has also a quest book, which updates when possible.

But, the night might come soon. So be prepared if any mobs spawn!
In this map there is also a Youtuber Hall. If you?re an youtuber and recorded the map, you might have a sign with your channel name and subs there! I look frequently for ppl that recorded it, so you can optionally submit your video link here. The lobby also has some rules, info and credits about the map!

title: Skyblock Classic [1.16.100+]
briefDescription: Welcome to Skyblock Classic! This map is based on the loved and old skyblock minigame. In a vast void, you are in a small L-shaped ...

crawledImageUrls.text: Welcome to Skyblock Classic! This map is based on the loved and old skyblock minigame. In a vast void, you are in a small L-shaped island, and a chest contains some resources you can use to start your advent?re. Also, it seems a tiny cactus is very far away, and perhaps you could make it useful too! With everything in hand, a journey starts.

The books are both optional, welcome one explains some things and introduces you to the map. The quest book contains more than 20 optional quests, each one having it?s own difficulty. The island has also a hidden chest, which you can get 2 saplings in case you haven?t got any from the starting tree. Also, cacti farms are possible, since there?s a cactus far away from the island. With everything in mind, here?s a recap from what stuff the map contains.
Anyways, i hope you enjoy the map! I had a lot of fun making it, specially the quests. This is my first map to be posted here, so i am a newbie. If you like it, i may post more maps!

crawledImageUrls.text: When I saw the ?Cubic World? map and I really wanted to play it on B?. But I didn?t find anything like it, and I will decide to recreate it.
This map is a cube world, which makes sense. You need to develop in it and just survive.
Resources are limited. There is a special villager in Hell who will help you survive!

The purpose of the map is development with limited resources. The world is very small, you only have a few trees at the start of survival, two biomes in the Regular world and four biomes in the Nether world. The ultimate goal is to kill the Ender Dragon. But it?s harder than usual as you need to find the hidden blaze spawner!
I don?t want to steal this card or anything like that. If you (the ?reator of the Cube World map) do not want this, then of course I delete it map .

Also, now there are two new biomes! Desert and winter forest!
